content:
Spring troubles?
...{短暂停}
Shedding season.

Grand Cross... conjunction aspect...
Following the arc of the sky...
Hmm? I'm just admiring the winter sky.{想象中}

The neighborhood where I used to live,
It should be spring now.{短暂停}
Oh, I don't really pay attention to seasons.

Ah-choo~! You know,
there's this ancient Eastern Astralink where, at this time of year...{短暂停}
foot bathing is quite popular as a wellness practice.

Things perfect for spring, let me think...{想象中}
Tea, bread, fragrances, flowers,
and spending all day reading by the floor-to-ceiling windows of a library.

What's perfect for a spring's day? Lemme think...{想象中}
Tea, bread, butterflies, flowers,
and spending all day reading in a sunlit library.

About what I wanted to talk to you about...{短暂停}
I was thinking how around this time each year,
I spend more time at the shop.

Then, my ears became more sensitive,
And many spring sounds, carried on warm breaths...{短暂停}
Made their way into my mind.

Grand Cross... conjunction aspect...
Following the arc of the heavens...
Hmm? I'm just admiring the winter sky.{想象中}

In spring, flower petals flutter around in the trees,
I just wanna swat at them with my paw! {短暂停}
What's wrong with punching flower petals anyway?
